			<a href="https://netblocks.org/reports" rel="category tag">Reports</a>			&middot; May 9, 2023		</div>
		<header class="entry-header">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://netblocks.org/reports/internet-disrupted-in-pakistan-amid-arrest-of-former-pm-imran-khan-JA6RmrAQ" rel="bookmark">Internet disrupted in Pakistan amid arrest of former PM Imran Khan</a></h2>		</header><!-- .entry-header -->
		<div class="entry-excerpt">
			<p>NetBlocks metrics confirm the disruption of Twitter, Facebook and YouTube on multiple internet providers in Pakistan on Tuesday 9 May 2023. Additionally, total internet shutdowns have been observed on mobile &#8230;</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	</div>

</article><!-- #post-## -->

													
